      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? This car is an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. I\u2019ve kept it in pristine, showroom-quality condition\u2014seriously, it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out! It drives like a cloud and has been babied since day one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
