    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear or age. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely no swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains firm and supple without a single crease, and the original 'new car' scent is still present. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history performed exclusively at the original dealership. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance sensors, functions perfectly. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any road debris or oxidation. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example that performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. I welcome any third-party inspections to verify its pristine state. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title.",
      "price": 44800.0,
